moduleGroup.name: Global Shape Analysis - Two Groups (Post Shape Reporter)

specify a directory into which shape files will be dumped; these shape files will be references in the scene files
if the directory doesn't exist, it will be created (assuming sufficient permissions)

output.name: Output
output.description:
specify a directory into which shape files will be dumped; these shape files will be references in the scene files
if the directory doesn't exist, it will be created (assuming sufficient permissions)

module.name: Choose Reference Subject
module.description: Connect the Shape Output Directory parameter of the group which contains the subject you wish to use as a reference for generating the scenes. Then enter the index of that subject within that group.
